4023  native_context()->set_intl_segment_iterator_map(*segment_iterator_map);
4024  }
4025  {
4026  // Set up the maps for SegmentDataObjects, with and without "isWordLike"
4027  // property.
4028  constexpr int kNumProperties = 3;
4029  constexpr int kNumPropertiesWithWordlike = kNumProperties + 1;
4030  constexpr int kInstanceSize =
4031  JSObject::kHeaderSize + kNumProperties * kTaggedSize;
4032  constexpr int kInstanceSizeWithWordlike =
4033  JSObject::kHeaderSize + kNumPropertiesWithWordlike * kTaggedSize;
4034  DirectHandle<Map> map = factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
4035  JS_OBJECT_TYPE, kInstanceSize, TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND,
4036  kNumProperties);
4037  DirectHandle<Map> map_with_wordlike =
4038  factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
4039  JS_OBJECT_TYPE, kInstanceSizeWithWordlike,
4040  TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND, kNumPropertiesWithWordlike);
4041  map->SetConstructor(native_context()->object_function());
4042  map_with_wordlike->SetConstructor(native_context()->object_function());
4043  map->set_prototype(*isolate_->initial_object_prototype());
4044  map_with_wordlike->set_prototype(*isolate_->initial_object_prototype());
4045  Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map, kNumProperties);
4046  Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map_with_wordlike,
4047  kNumPropertiesWithWordlike);
4048  int index = 0;
4049  { // segment
4050  Descriptor d =
4051  Descriptor::DataField(isolate_, factory->segment_string(),
4052  index++, NONE, Representation::Tagged());
4053  map->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4054  map_with_wordlike->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4055  }
4056  { // index
4057  Descriptor d =
4058  Descriptor::DataField(isolate_, factory->index_string(), index++,
4059  NONE, Representation::Tagged());
4060  map->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4061  map_with_wordlike->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4062  }
4063  { // input
4064  Descriptor d =
4065  Descriptor::DataField(isolate_, factory->input_string(), index++,
4066  NONE, Representation::Tagged());
4067  map->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4068  map_with_wordlike->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4069  }
4070  DCHECK_EQ(index, kNumProperties);
4071  { // isWordLike
4072  Descriptor d =
4073  Descriptor::DataField(isolate_, factory->isWordLike_string(),
4074  index++, NONE, Representation::Tagged());
4075  map_with_wordlike->AppendDescriptor(isolate_, &d);
4076  }
4077  DCHECK_EQ(index, kNumPropertiesWithWordlike);
4078  DCHECK(!map->is_dictionary_map());
4079  DCHECK(!map_with_wordlike->is_dictionary_map());
4080  native_context()->set_intl_segment_data_object_map(*map);
4081  native_context()->set_intl_segment_data_object_wordlike_map(
4082  *map_with_wordlike);
4083  }
4084  }
4085
